          "action": "request_more_info",
          "handoffTarget": "provisioning_engineering",
          "rationale": "Three identical failures indicate a data or network-element configuration defect the flow-through engine cannot resolve; blind retries only widen the fallout window."
        },
        {
          "trigger": "Simple port-in still pending past the one-business-day FCC simple-port interval",
          "action": "escalate_to_human",
          "handoffTarget": "lnp_operations_desk",
          "rationale": "Ports beyond the mandated interval create regulatory exposure and are the leading driver of day-one churn on acquisition; the LNP desk owns inter-carrier escalation with the losing carrier."
        }
